The MNIST database of handwritten digits is available at http://yann.lecun.com/exdb/mnist/

In order to install the required files, a shell script can be executed:
$ ./setup_mnist.sh

This shell script will:
- download train-images-idx3-ubyte.gz
- download train-labels-idx1-ubyte.gz
- download t10k-images-idx3-ubyte.gz
- download t10k-labels-idx1-ubyte.gz
- gunzip train-images-idx3-ubyte.gz
- gunzip train-labels-idx1-ubyte.gz
- gunzip t10k-images-idx3-ubyte.gz
- gunzip t10k-labels-idx1-ubyte.gz
